  "texts": [
    "An increasing number of AI academics in psychology are teaming up with AI professionals to influence future AI development by learning more about the mental processes that underpin how people think about and interact with AI.",
    "The third broad category includes research into AI's capacity for individualization.",
    "When it comes to artificial intelligence and online advertising, this field is well established.",
    "The many parts can enrich one another.",
    "For instance, data-driven model research can benefit from adopting AI with a personalization function like that utilized in digital marketing."
  ]
}